comments: Shes a sweet lady, but honestly its a hard course for those that don\'t understand biology very well. Being a 100 level I thought it wouldn\'t be as hard, but it is. Her notes barely help with the quizzes and tests.
Wonderful teacher!! Biology isn\'t my favorite but she made it easy. She will help when asked will go over answers for quizes. Take her!!

dont have to attend. this class is somewhat hard since her notes do not in my opinion go with the quizzes or test at all. must use google and textbook to find correct answers or atleast have some decent background with biology.

Loved ms Gugino! Shes funny and very helpful if you don\'t understand something. Attendance isn\'t mandatory but her lectures are pretty much the answers to the questions about to be on the quizzes and exams. Everything is online too. I would definitely recommend her!
Though her attendance wasn\'t mandatory, I always found it helpful to go since she likes to add notes on the chalkboard throughout her lectures that are not on the powerpoint.

Gugino is a very nice lady, but if you aren\'t already good at Biology, BIO 100 may not be the "easy A" you\'re hoping for. Attendance is mandatory. I attended every single class and took notes, but her notes are very vague. I ended up searching for test answers on Google all semester. 15 quizzes total and 5 exams, all taken online.

She is very nice and very understanding. Exams are all online and for hour class we had 15 quizzes that were online and the worst 5 get dropped. Nice class, even though you don\'t have to go. But if you do go you will do better on the exams and quizzes.

Gugino is an okay professor. tests and quizes are all online, definitely have a group of three to take quizes and tests. keep the quizes because most of the questions that are on the test are from quizes. she doesnt go over everything mostly i had to look up every answer online because her notes didnt help what so ever.

Easiest class ive taken in college. Attendance isnt mandatory, I went to maybe 6 classes. Quizzes and tests are online. Both are really easy if you read the book. Final was cake too, finished in maybe 15 minutes and received a solid B on it. Study the quizzes!
i never understood bio, but she made it so easy!!! going to class and then skimming the chapters made my life easy!! great teacher!!

Thank God for BIO 100. Honestly it was an easy A!!! I am telling you now, Take the class with her. You don?t have to show up for class, and the quizzes and test are online, so it is easier for you to cheat lol. She is really nice and pretty. The only thing that was tricky is that the test and quizzes sometimes, but beside that, good class.

I Love this teacher. She is easy to talk to and she don\'t mind helping students out. I hated biology with a passion but she made it fun and interesting. She give quizes take home quizes. On top of being very educated she is also smoking hot. Attendance is not mandatory but I came everyday because she is so beatiful and I wanted to learn more

She is really nice and understanding. She answers all questions and is very approachable. The only thing that was tricky is that the test and quiz questions are worded a little wierd. Overall she \'s a great teacher that knows her stuff!
Very interesting and knows a lot about the subject, tests are easy if you attend class and do the quizzes

Suuuuper nice! You really can\'t fail, she gave a lot of quizzes incase ppl did bad on the tests...i didn\'t buy the book and got a B, she posts all the notes and her tests ususally consist of questions from the quizzes! Very approachable!
Good class in all, only thing that was not cool is she sprung a group assignment and oral presentation that was not in the syllabus. But it was pretty easy to get a good grade. Super nice prof!
Great class. Easy to follow. She posts the guided notes on ANGEL. very approachable, very knowledgable. I strongly recomend her class
